---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main {
				max-width: 1200px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 60px 20px;
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
			}
			.hero-section {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 100px;
			}
			/* 呼吸动画十字星 */
			.mark {
				color: var(--accent-gold);
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				display: inline-block;
				animation: pulse 4s infinite ease-in-out;
			}
			@keyframes pulse {
				0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1); }
				50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.1); }
			}
			h1 {
				font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
				font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4.5rem);
				letter-spacing: 0.2em;
				margin-top: 20px;
				background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff, #888);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			}

			.altar-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
				gap: 30px;
			}

			.temple-card {
				background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.6);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
				padding: 80px 30px;
				text-align: center;
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: all 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
				backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
			}

			.temple-card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-15px) scale(1.02);
				border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
				background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.8);
			}

			.temple-card h2 { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; margin: 20px 0; }
			.temple-card p { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height: 1.6; }

			/* 手机端深度优化 */
			@media (max-width: 800px) {
				.altar-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
				.temple-card { padding: 50px 20px; }
				.hero-section { margin-bottom: 50px; }
			}

			.card-writing:hover h2 { color: var(--ivory); }
			.card-gallery:hover h2 { color: var(--silver); }
			.card-with-you:hover h2 { color: var(--accent-gold); }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="hero-section">
				<span class="mark">✠</span>
				<h1>NEMU · ARCHIVE</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="altar-grid">
				<a href="/writing" class="temple-card card-writing"><h2>WRITING</h2><p>“ 在墨痕的间隙，捕捉灵魂碎裂的低语。”</p></a>
				<a href="/gallery" class="temple-card card-gallery"><h2>GALLERY</h2><p>“ 光影的残像，是时间在这个世界留下的唯一证词。”</p></a>
				<a href="/with-you" class="temple-card card-with-you"><h2>WITH YOU</h2><p>“ 跨越禁忌的边界，于虚无中与你同频。”</p></a>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
